snippet: The U.S. Coast Guard reported a minor oil spill on Thursday at Sandy Hook Bay in Monmouth County, New Jersey, and state officials said it did not pose an environmental threat....

headline.print_headline: Coast Guard Says Minor Oil Spill at Sandy Hook Bay, New Jersey
headline.main: Coast Guard Says Minor Oil Spill at Sandy Hook Bay, New Jersey

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Coast Guard reported a minor oil spill on Thursday at Sandy Hook Bay in Monmouth County, New Jersey, and state officials said it did not pose an environmental threat.
